sourcesContent: function r(){let i=[],o=[],t={enqueue(e){o.push(e)},requestAnimationFrame(...e){let a=requestAnimationFrame(...e);t.add(()=>cancelAnimationFrame(a))},nextFrame(...e){t.requestAnimationFrame(()=>{t.requestAnimationFrame(...e)})},setTimeout(...e){let a=setTimeout(...e);t.add(()=>clearTimeout(a))},add(e){i.push(e)},dispose(){for(let e of i.splice(0))e()},async workQueue(){for(let e of o.splice(0))await e()}};return t}export{r as disposables};
